You can read all the books you want, but to have a child with special needs is a whole different story. &#8220;Consumed with grief, fear and worry, I was very unsure of what the future would hold for me as her mother and the challenges we would face as a family, but this is the child God gave us. &#8220;I could feel the connection from the very beginning.There is so much darkness in this world, I know people need to be reminded of the good. Mbali is the good,&#8221; Daphne says.